Q) FIND THE WINNING PERCENTAGE OF 'Mumbai Indians'

a = df_p[(df_p['team1'] == 'Mumbai Indians') | (df_p['team2'] == 'Mumbai Indians')]
b = a[a['winner'] == 'Mumbai Indians']

print(len(b)/ len(a)*100)        /* it is nearly 60 percent */ 

