Q) FIND THE PERCENTAGE OF MATCHES WHERE TOSS WINNER WON THE MATCH

a = df_p[df_p['toss_winner'] == df_p['winner']]
b = df_p['id'].nunique()

print((len(a)/b)*100)              /* nearly 51 percent */ 
